title: CoreAVC Professional Edition v1.6.5.0
description:
The CoreCodec CoreAVC High Definition H.264 video codec is based on the MPEG-4 Part 10 standard 
and is one of the codecs used in Blu-ray and in HD-DVD. AVC / H.264 is the next-generation standard for video, 
and CoreAVC? is being recognized as being the world&#039;s fastest H.264 software video decoder.

The efficiency of CoreAVC in &#039;software&#039; is often compared to be faster than other solutions 
that try to rely on &#039;hardware&#039; to increase playback performance of H.264 video.
